{"tid":2078768,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警稱無位騷編號 大狀轟辱官智慧","createTime":"2020-06-25T09:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T10:25:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d23a477ec0de7edc94746fd42bd152f088fb38ac","tid":2078768,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:53:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200625/CHT3RMA2GBRPM64XQ6NOJFV7WA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200625%2FCHT3RMA2GBRPM64XQ6NOJFV7WA%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfeF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=40b1b251\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200625%2FCHT3RMA2GBRPM64XQ6NOJFV7WA%2F&h=6513cb33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200625/CHT3RMA2GBRPM64XQ6NOJFV7WA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警稱無位騷編號 大狀轟辱官智慧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/E_Ptv6cdGflebTE8E4CB9VBwTrQ=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UJTOURTKIJ3O6TYAAXOTN2F3MU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FE_Ptv6cdGflebTE8E4CB9VBwTrQ%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUJTOURTKIJ3O6TYAAXOTN2F3MU.jpg&h=80a46877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部份申請人昨在庭外示威，抗議警員隱藏識別編號執法。<br />\n<br />\n【司法覆核案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反修例運動至今，警方執勤時經常隱藏識別編號，包括專門應付大型活動的「速龍小隊」。市民和記協均對警方提出司法覆核，高院昨合併五宗案件審理。庭上透露，警方重提速龍小隊服裝沒位置展示編號，申請方斥說法「侮辱智慧」，並陳述有報稱受警暴所害的市民因無法識別警員投訴無門，認為不展示編號違反人權法。<br />\n<br />\n案件由法官周家明主審。資深大律師李柱銘代表七旬翁陳基裘和中槍教師楊子俊，炮轟政府至今未盡披露責任，交代由誰決定警察突然不用展示編號及決定理由，有違公義。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指違反人權法<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：飛虎隊員申匿名被官質疑<br />\n<br />\n警隊總督察在誓章提到，2016年暴動案件後，警方為速龍小隊從海外<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n「侮辱法官智慧」。李亦指，2017年已採用新戰衣，證明不展示編號與去年的警察起底問題無關。<br />\n<br />\n李續說，總警司謝振中和監警會主席梁定邦曾表示，警方不展示編號的<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n，斥答辯方：「咁嘅嘢都仲喺法庭同我拗，仲唔起身認錯！」<br />\n<br />\n資深大律師潘熙指，申請人陳恭信、魯湛思和吳康聯報稱受警察襲擊，惟無<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n《警察通例》中關於展示編號和委任證的指引，反映是故意的決定。<br />\n<br />\n潘熙指警方去年雖採用新的「行動呼號」，但現實環境中，<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n防酷刑和殘忍、侮辱的對待，展示編號是必要問責措施。<br />\n<br />\n資深大律師戴啟思代表香港記者協會，指投訴警方的機制有缺陷，<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n察問責，會阻嚇記者採訪公眾活動。聆訊明續。<br />\n案件編號：HCAL1747、1753、2671、2703、2915/19"},{"pid":"44928a31dcb0eedda83b8bacac7ae50976e2a169","tid":2078768,"uid":11291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:54:19.000Z","msg":"黑警：法律？咩嚟嫁？食得嫁？"},{"pid":"ec8594ab224acbd17c05cd2ac51ef8749dd1732b","tid":2078768,"uid":199893,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"香港小姐泳衣環節都show到number<br />\n班狗show唔到係可以理解嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f246723e7a38a6b2597917b7d3dec987627004","tid":2078768,"uid":104128,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:56:52.000Z","msg":"1999咁....完全睇唔明"},{"pid":"e91b6971d40b032d4e53f8e0e5bd6d7e9144d457","tid":2078768,"uid":78392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:57:16.000Z","msg":"咁嘅嘢都仲喺法庭同我拗，仲唔起身認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1437bbd51e6f4ecdc1aa86f7b5f886b409742a90","tid":2078768,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"香港冇警察 得公安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ca9565272a7dc7e098c4d7cd22821b0f6db2fe","tid":2078768,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:58:45.000Z","msg":"點解依家貼新聞要咁多。。。。。"},{"pid":"d3a37d359f7196f278f641491521053bdf4db066","tid":2078768,"uid":54721,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"68ca9565272a7dc7e098c4d7cd22821b0f6db2fe